 must now figure out how to survive and let the folks back on Earth know he is alive and needs rescue. This is hard-science science fiction. Parts of it read like really complicated (but amusing) word problems, juggling mass and time and weight, etc. But all of that adds to the realism. You can tell Andy Weir loves his space exploration and knows a ton about it. He totally had me convinced, anyway. The Martian is a fast read, and the main character’s irrepressible sense of humor will have you cheering for him as he tries to survive against impossible odds. I will also never eat another potato again. (Long story.) If you’re looking for a fast-paced, believable space adventure set in present day, this is your book.","rating":5,"shelving":{"__typename":"Shelving","shelf":{"__typename":"Shelf","name":"read","webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/list/25375513?shelf=read"},"taggings":[],"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1344360506"},"likeCount":878,"viewerHasLiked":null,"commentCount":23,"viewerCanComment({\"resourceType\":\"review\"})":null},"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.Pyl2r3GzETT0W-Hvwk0bhA":{"id":"kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.Pyl2r3GzETT0W-Hvwk0bhA","__typename":"Contributor","works":{"__typename":"ContributorWorksConnection","totalCount":91}},"User:2040005":{"id":2040005,"__typename":"User","legacyId":2040005,"imageUrlSquare":"https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/users/1356706506i/2040005._UX200_CR0,25,200,200_.jpg","isAuthor":true,"textReviewsCount":83,"viewableName":"Wil Wheaton","isBlockedByViewer":false,"webUrl":"https://www.goodreads.com/user/show/2040005-wil-wheaton","contributor":{"__ref":"Contributor:kca://author/amzn1.gr.author.v1.Pyl2r3GzETT0W-Hvwk0bhA"},"isFollowing":false,"isFriend":false,"followersCount":174546},"Review:kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.vyJ1NKJ4IIuXKbloqsWyAA":{"id":"kca://review:goodreads/amzn1.gr.review:goodreads.v1.vyJ1NKJ4IIuXKbloqsWyAA","__typename":"